oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 7th Annual Woody Guthrie Birthday Celebration (2005)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Birthdays; Guthrie, Woody, 1912-1967; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (brown on white) announcing Chicago's Seventh Annual Woody Guthrie Birthday Celebration featuring Bucky Halker, Janet Bean, Anna Fermin, Tom "Pickles" Piekarski, Steve Dawson, Chris Waltz, and Kat Eggleston, and hosted by Tom Jackson, at Martyrs on July 15. Poster features a metal photoplate of Woody Guthrie.
